# Project Rules

<!-- These rules are prepended to all agent system prompts by Lauren Loop. -->
<!-- Rename this file to project-rules.md and customize for your project. -->

## Critical Rules

1. **No mock data.** If external services fail, return error messages. Never generate fake responses.
2. **`.env` is read-only.** Never modify without explicit approval.
3. **No new endpoints.** Modify existing endpoints and scripts. Maintain backward compatibility.

